data.description: Price Reduction. Looking for a home with a salt water screened, in ground pool? A large carport with enclosed storage and electric? Look no further because this is your home! These amenities are top reasons to buy but it gets better as this home was built for entertaining. Enjoy the spacious great room with bar* and conversation area, kitchen with seating for six plus a breakfast bar, and a split-level floor plan that separates the guest bedrooms from the master. The location offers easy access to Gulf Shores or Foley and is near two full-care hospitals. Just 12 miles to the beach, this house is a must see!!  This property is located in the County and the association has few restrictions regarding boats and RV's, refer to the documents.
